=================
Bugs:
=================
+ [CRITICAL] _nextID declared static in bill.h - each .c file gets its own copy,
  causing key collisions when loading a file then adding new bills.
  Fix: declare extern in bill.h, define once in bill.c
+ [CRITICAL] ExportAsCSV doesn't check if fopen returns NULL - will crash on failure
  Fix: add NULL guard same as ExportAsTXT
+ [CRITICAL] igText(fileName) in ui_menubar.c is a format string vulnerability
  Fix: igText("%s", fileName)
+ strcpy(budgetName, fileName) in BudgetSave/SaveEntryMap - potential buffer overflow
  Fix: use snprintf(budgetName, sizeof(budgetName), "%s", fileName)
+ RemoveEntry shifts keys while iterating the stb_ds map - unsafe, backing array
  may reallocate mid-loop. Fix: collect keys to shift first, then modify.
+ GetEntryMapString static buffer (4096 bytes) overflows at ~21 bills
  Fix: increase buffer size or use dynamic allocation
+ fread return values not checked in LoadEntryMap / BudgetLoad - corrupt .bud files
  will silently load garbage or spin in a huge loop
+ CSV export doesn't escape bill names - commas/quotes/newlines corrupt the output
  Fix: wrap fields in quotes and escape internal quotes
+ Duplicate load logic between LoadEntryMap (bill.c) and BudgetLoad (export.c)
  LoadEntryMap appears unused - consider removing it
+ SDL window title says "Budget App" instead of "Mojo Budget"

